Best Practice for You

For every problem:

First solve normally
Add thread names
Print thread states
Add delays using sleep()
Break code intentionally
Fix synchronization issues

That’s where real understanding happens.

Strong Recommendation

Start with these 5 first:

Number printing thread
Even/Odd threads
join() example
Bank account synchronization
Producer Consumer

If you master these, your threading foundation becomes strong.

